8</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.spotlights.news/09d26c6a1d9d759af89848f2a07f6d97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.spotlights.news%2F09d26c6a1d9d759af89848f2a07f6d97.jpg&h=a063b283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://taiwan-swine.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=9115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftaiwan-swine.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D9115&d=NL7x4a%2B2tDO30sNGYm3nWr5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=04522f13\" target=\"_blank\">http://taiwan-swine.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=9115</a><br />\n2008-5-20 13:20:20<br />\n還有一種心理上的世界地圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/_PeCbUskd_wY/ReWh4TKYl8I/AAAAAAAAAmk/kGbl5HqsQa8/s1600/heart_map.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F_PeCbUskd_wY%2FReWh4TKYl8I%2FAAAAAAAAAmk%2FkGbl5HqsQa8%2Fs1600%2Fheart_map.jpg&h=a3ae8bf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc49f3abbafacb6d3ead90f51c0e9f4e70e1b979","tid":965095,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T18:56:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/台客\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh%2F%E5%8F%B0%E5%AE%A2&d=NL7x4a%2B2tDO30sNGYm3nWr5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=04b4cb63\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/台客</a><br />\n<br />\n台客，為一種帶有歧視之貶義性名詞，早期原本為台灣外省籍人士對台灣本省人士的帶有歧視之貶稱。"},{"pid":"919a04b3d798ee7dd12ca36df745a9382bffe7fd","tid":965095,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T19:06:58.000Z","msg":"以前台灣論壇見過呢張圖 <br />\nVitas<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6224c50e87871dbc652c630bc006cb867a6c21","tid":965095,"uid":6007,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T19:36:09.000Z","msg":"嘟嘟嚕都大大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/